From: BORE fair.c upgrade - defaults, inheritance, hub/stub
Subject: fair.c only - BORE v5 upgrade (sched.h+futex+features done manually)

Upgrades fair.c with:
- New default values (offset=24, scale=1536, cache=75M)
- sched_burst_inherit_type (0=none, 1=parent, 2=hub/stub)
- sched_burst_smoothness (unified 0-3, falls back to legacy)
- Hub/stub ancestor inheritance
- Thread group inheritance
- fork_burst_penalty in fair.c
- sched_bore_update_handler, inherit_type handler
- PREEMPT_SHORT_BORE check in yield

---
 kernel/sched/fair.c | 170 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---
 1 file changed, 159 insertions(+), 11 deletions(-)

